Quick start

Install F Droid
https://f-droid.org/packages/com.termux/

then, install Termux and Termux:wedget

then, copy-paste and enter in Termux:
curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yasuhito3/Sonia-for-Android/main/install.sh | bash



if you want to make a wedget, install Termux:wedget, then copy-paste in termux and enter



mkdir -p ~/.shortcuts
cat > ~/.shortcuts/Musica << 'EOF'
#!/data/data/com.termux/files/usr/bin/bash
musica
EOF
chmod +x ~/.shortcuts/Musica

then

Long-press on Android-Screen and add a Termux:wedget

end//
